  "original_lang": "ta",
  "original_title": "\u0bae\u0ba9\u0bcd\u0ba9\u0bbe\u0bb0\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0baa\u0bcb\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1\u0bb5\u0bb0\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bc1 \u0b9a\u0bc7\u0bb5\u0bc8\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bcd \u0ba4\u0b9f\u0bc8\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bae\u0bc8\u0baf\u0bbe\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0b86\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0bb0\u0bae\u0b9f\u0bc8\u0ba8\u0bcd\u0ba4 \u0bae\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bcd : \u0bb5\u0bc7\u0b9f\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc8 \u0baa\u0bbe\u0bb0\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4 \u0baa\u0bca\u0bb2\u0bbf\u0bb8\u0bbe\u0bb0\u0bcd",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "People enraged by suspension of transport services in Mannar: Police were amused",
      "author": "Digital Desk 5",
      "body_lines": [
        "In Mannar today Tuesday (12) morning, people suffered massively due to the protest led by the Mannar Private Bus Association.",
        "The private bus owners blocked the road with their buses so that the government transport service could not be carried forward.",
        "Due to this, there was an argument between the people and the private bus association, and the people expressed their strong opposition to the parking of private buses in the middle of the road so that the government transport service could not be carried out, and they demanded that the said private bus be removed from that place and action should be taken to carry out the government transport service.",
        "However, due to the fact that the private transport association did not take steps to promote smooth transport services, the people who were waiting for a long time for the bus engaged in arguments and tried to remove the private buses that were blocking the road so that the government transport service could not be carried out.",
        "Then the people took steps to remove the said buses from the place. Then the owners of the said private buses took the said buses away from the place.",
        "After that, after a long time, the government transport services resumed as usual.",
        "However, the people have expressed their displeasure that the protest by the private transport associations should have been carried out in a way that did not affect the general public.",
        "The concerned party had requested to supply the Mannar District Private Transport Society buses with the diesel supplied to the Mannar depot.",
        "However, only 2413 liters of diesel has been provided to private buses in the recently provided diesel.",
        "The private bus association owners requested diesel from the Mannar depot authorities but it was not provided.",
        "In this situation, on the morning of the 5th, the private buses were engaged in a work inspection and they blocked the road with the private buses so that they could not carry out the government transport service and demanded to provide fuel for them.",
        "As a result, transport services were completely disrupted for some time and people faced various inconveniences.",
        "In this situation, a special discussion took place between the government and private transport association representatives under the leadership of Chief Minister Mrs. A.Sranli D Mel at the Mannar District Secretariat.",
        "Divisional Secretary, Army and Police high officials were present in the discussion.",
        "It was agreed during the discussion that according to the government's position of supplying diesel to private bus service buses from Sri Lanka Transport Board's oil tanks, if 6600 liters of diesel is supplied to Mannar road, 2500 liters of diesel and 5000 liters of diesel to private bus services if E13 is 200 liters of diesel.",
        "In this situation, the boycott protest initiated by the private bus association owners was abandoned.",
        "Even though they inquired with the relevant parties regarding this matter, they did not take appropriate action.",
        "This is the situation today, Tuesday (12) morning, the private transport associations stopped the transport service and engaged in protest.",
        "It is worth noting that even though the incident took place in Mannar Bazar area which affected the public since Tuesday (12th) morning, the police and special task forces who came to the place looked at the problems and did not take any efforts to prevent them."
      ],
